  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nMy sepolia validator gets killed by the system because it uses up the entire memory and swap (\"killed\").\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nShould be able to handle 100 validators on a machine with 32 GB of RAM. (I was using the same machine to run 20k Prater validators with Teku before.)\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\n```\r\n./lodestar account validator import --network sepolia --directory ../staking-deposit-cli/sepolia-genesis-100/validator_keys --passphraseFile ./pass.txt\r\n./lodestar validator --network \"sepolia\" --graffiti \"Goerli Nunki @q9f Lodestar\" --defaultFeeRecipient \"0xff58d746a67c2e42bcc07d6b3f58406e8837e883\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\n\r\n```\r\n~/lodestar tags/v0.38.1* user@nunki 9s                                                                                                                                                                                           \r\n‚ùØ ./validator.sh                                                                                                                                                                                                                 \r\nJun-20 11:41:53.922[]                 info: Lodestar network=sepolia, version=v0.38.1/5cb67b1, commit=5cb67b11b08266d4982157f19f1de21643168b84\r\n./lodestar: line 7: 1694859 Killed                  node --trace-deprecation --max-old-space-size=4096 ./packages/cli/bin/lodestar.js \"$@\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n\r\n- OS: Archlinux\r\n- Version: v0.38.1\r\n- Branch: tag v0.38.1\r\n- Commit hash: 5cb67b11b08266d4982157f19f1de21643168b84",
